{
  "video_id": "30kPKxGuHLA",
  "title": "Paul Romer: The world's first charter city?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "In 2007,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "I decided that we needed to reconceptualize"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "how we thought about economic development."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "Our new goal should be"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "that when every family thinks about where they want to live and work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "they should be able to choose between"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "at least a handful"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "of different cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 35260.0,
      "text": "that were all competing to attract new residents."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35260.0,
      "end_time": 38260.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;re a long way away from that goal right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38260.0,
      "end_time": 41260.0,
      "text": "There are billions of people in developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41260.0,
      "end_time": 44260.0,
      "text": "who don&#39;t have even a single city that would be willing to welcome them."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "But the amazing thing about cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "is they&#39;re worth so much more"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "than it costs to build them."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "So we could easily supply the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "with dozens, maybe hundreds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "of new cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "Now this might sound preposterous to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;ve never thought about new cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "But just substitute apartment building for cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 66259.0,
      "text": "Imagine half the people who wanted to be in apartments already had them;"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66260.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "the other half aren&#39;t there yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "You could try and expand the capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "by doing additions on all the existing apartments."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "But you know what you&#39;d run into"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "is those apartments and the surrounding areas"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "have rules to avoid discomfort"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "and the distractions of construction."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s extremely hard to do all of those additions."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "But you could go out someplace brand new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "build a brand new apartment building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "as long as the rules there"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "were ones that facilitated construction"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "rather than getting in the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "So I proposed"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "that governments create new reform zones"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "big enough to hold cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "and gave them a name: charter cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "Later I learned that at about this same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 110260.0,
      "text": "Javier and Octavio"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "were thinking about the challenge of reform"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "in Honduras."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 118260.0,
      "text": "They knew that about 75,000 Hondurans every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 118260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "would leave to go to the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "and they wanted to ask, what could they do"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "to make sure that those people could stay"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 127260.0,
      "text": "and do the same things in Honduras."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 127260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "At one point, Javier said to Octavio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "\"What if we took some of our empty land --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "what if we just gave it to an embassy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "give some to the U.S. embassy; give some to the Canadian embassy --"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "and then if people want to go work"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "under the rules of Canada or under the rules of the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 142260.0,
      "text": "they can go get jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 142260.0,
      "end_time": 144260.0,
      "text": "do everything they do on those embassy grounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 144260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "that they would otherwise have to go to Canada or the U.S. to do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "In the summer of 2009,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "Honduras went through a wrenching constitutional crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "At the next regularly scheduled election,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "Pepe Lobo won in a landslide"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "on a platform that promised reform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "but reconciliation as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "He asked Octavio to be his chief of staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, I was getting ready"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "to give a talk at TEDGlobal."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "Through a process of refinement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "trial and error, a lot of user testing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "I tried to boil this complicated concept of charter city"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 184260.0,
      "text": "down to the bare essentials."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "The first point was the importance of rules,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "like those rules that say"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t come in and disturb all the existing apartment holders."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "We pay a lot of attention to new technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 197260.0,
      "text": "but it takes technologies and rules to get progress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 197260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s usually the rules that hold us back."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "In the fall of 2010, a friend from Guatemala"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "sent Octavio a link to the TEDTalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "He showed it to Javier."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "They called me."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 214260.0,
      "text": "They said, \"Let&#39;s present this to the leaders of our country.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 214260.0,
      "end_time": 217260.0,
      "text": "So in December we met in Miami,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 217260.0,
      "end_time": 219260.0,
      "text": "in a hotel conference room."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 219260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "I tried to explain this point"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "about how valuable cities are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "how much more valuable they are than they cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "And I used this slide"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "showing how valuable the raw land is"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "in a place like New York City:"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "notice, land that&#39;s worth thousands of dollars, in some cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "per square meter."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "But it was a fairly abstract discussion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "and at some point when there was a pause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "Octavio said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "\"Paul, maybe we could watch the TEDTalk.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "(Laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "So the TEDTalk laid out in very simple terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "a charter city is a place"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "where you start with uninhabited land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "a charter that specifies the rules that will apply there"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "and then a chance for people to opt in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "to go live under those rules or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "So I was asked by the president of Honduras"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "who said that we need to do this project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "this is important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "this could be the way forward for our country."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "I was asked to come to Tegucigalpa"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "and talk again on January fourth and fifth."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "So I presented"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "another fact-filled lecture"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 287260.0,
      "text": "that included a slide like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 287260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "which tried to make the point that, if you want to create a lot of value in a city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "it has to be very big."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 294260.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of Denver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 294260.0,
      "end_time": 296260.0,
      "text": "and the outline is the new airport that was built in Denver."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 296260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "This airport alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "covers more than 100 square kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 302260.0,
      "text": "So I was trying to persuade the Hondurans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 302260.0,
      "end_time": 304260.0,
      "text": "if you build a new city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got to start with a site that&#39;s at least 1,000 square kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s more than 250 hundred-thousand acres."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "Everybody applauded politely."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 317260.0,
      "text": "The faces in the audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 317260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "were very serious and attentive."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "The leader of the congress came up on stage and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "\"Professor Romer, thank you very much for your lecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "but maybe we could watch the TEDTalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 332260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got it here on my laptop.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "So I sat down, and they played the TEDTalk."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "And it got to the essence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "which is that a new city could offer new choices for people."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 343260.0,
      "text": "There would be a choice of a city which you could go to"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 343260.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "which could be in Honduras,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 347260.0,
      "text": "instead of hundreds of miles away in the North."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 349260.0,
      "text": "And it also involved new choices for leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 349260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "Because the leaders in the government there in Honduras"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 354260.0,
      "text": "would need help from partner countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 354260.0,
      "end_time": 356260.0,
      "text": "who could benefit from partner countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 356260.0,
      "end_time": 359260.0,
      "text": "who help them set up the rules in this charter and the enforcement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 359260.0,
      "end_time": 361260.0,
      "text": "so everybody can trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 361260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "that the charter really will be enforced."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 366260.0,
      "text": "And the insight of President Lobo"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 366260.0,
      "end_time": 369260.0,
      "text": "was that that assurance of enforcement"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 369260.0,
      "end_time": 371260.0,
      "text": "that I was thinking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 371260.0,
      "end_time": 374260.0,
      "text": "as a way to get the foreign investors to come in and build the city"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 374260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "could be equally important for all the different parties in Honduras"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 379260.0,
      "text": "who had suffered for so many years"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 379260.0,
      "end_time": 381260.0,
      "text": "from fear and distrust."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 381260.0,
      "end_time": 383260.0,
      "text": "We went and looked at a site."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 383260.0,
      "end_time": 385260.0,
      "text": "This picture&#39;s from there."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 385260.0,
      "end_time": 388260.0,
      "text": "It easily could hold a thousand square kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 388260.0,
      "end_time": 391260.0,
      "text": "And shortly thereafter, on January 19th,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 391260.0,
      "end_time": 394260.0,
      "text": "they voted in the congress to amend their constitution"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 394260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "to have a constitutional provision"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "that allows for special development regions."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 401260.0,
      "text": "In a country which had just gone through this wrenching crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 401260.0,
      "end_time": 404260.0,
      "text": "the vote in the congress in favor of this constitutional amendment"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 404260.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "was 124 to one."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 407260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "All parties, all factions in society, backed this."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 413260.0,
      "text": "To be part of the constitution, you actually have to pass it twice in the congress."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 413260.0,
      "end_time": 416260.0,
      "text": "On February 17th they passed it again"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 416260.0,
      "end_time": 419260.0,
      "text": "with another vote of 114 to one."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 419260.0,
      "end_time": 421260.0,
      "text": "Immediately after that vote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 421260.0,
      "end_time": 424260.0,
      "text": "on February 21st to the 24th,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 424260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "a delegation of about 30 Hondurans"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 428260.0,
      "text": "went to the two places in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 428260.0,
      "end_time": 430260.0,
      "text": "that are most interested in getting into the city building business."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 430260.0,
      "end_time": 432260.0,
      "text": "One is South Korea."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 432260.0,
      "end_time": 434260.0,
      "text": "This is a picture of a big, new city center"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 436260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s being built in South Korea --"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 436260.0,
      "end_time": 438260.0,
      "text": "bigger than downtown Boston."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 438260.0,
      "end_time": 440260.0,
      "text": "Everything you see there was built in four years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 440260.0,
      "end_time": 443260.0,
      "text": "after they spent four years getting the permits."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "The other place that&#39;s very interested in city building is Singapore."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve actually built two cities already in China"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "and are preparing the third."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "So if you think about this practically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 454260.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s where we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 454260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ve got a site; they&#39;re already thinking about this site for the second city."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re putting in place a legal system"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "that could allow for managers to come in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 463260.0,
      "text": "and also an external legal system."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 463260.0,
      "end_time": 466260.0,
      "text": "One country has already volunteered to let its supreme court"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 466260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "be the court of final appeal for the new judicial system there."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s designers and builders of cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "who are very interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "They even can bring with them some financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 477260.0,
      "text": "But the one thing you know they&#39;ve already solved"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 477260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "is that there&#39;s lots of tenants."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 482260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s lots of businesses that would like to locate in the Americas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 482260.0,
      "end_time": 484260.0,
      "text": "especially in a place with a free trade zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 484260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s lots of people who&#39;d like to go there."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "Around the world, there&#39;s 700 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 489260.0,
      "end_time": 492260.0,
      "text": "who say they&#39;d like to move permanently someplace else right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 492260.0,
      "end_time": 494260.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a million a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 494260.0,
      "end_time": 496260.0,
      "text": "who leave Latin America to go to the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 496260.0,
      "end_time": 498260.0,
      "text": "Many of these are a father"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 498260.0,
      "end_time": 500260.0,
      "text": "who has to leave his family behind to go get a job --"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 500260.0,
      "end_time": 502260.0,
      "text": "sometimes a single mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 502260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "who has to get enough money to even pay for food or clothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 507260.0,
      "text": "Sadly, sometimes there are even children"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 507260.0,
      "end_time": 509260.0,
      "text": "who are trying to get reunited with their parents"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 509260.0,
      "end_time": 513260.0,
      "text": "that they haven&#39;t seen, in some cases, for a decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 516260.0,
      "text": "So what kind of an idea is it"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 516260.0,
      "end_time": 518260.0,
      "text": "to think about building a brand new city in Honduras?"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 518260.0,
      "end_time": 520260.0,
      "text": "Or to build a dozen of these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 520260.0,
      "end_time": 522260.0,
      "text": "or a hundred of these, around the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 522260.0,
      "end_time": 524260.0,
      "text": "What kind of an idea is it"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 524260.0,
      "end_time": 526260.0,
      "text": "to think about insisting"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 526260.0,
      "end_time": 529260.0,
      "text": "that every family have a choice of several cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 529260.0,
      "end_time": 532260.0,
      "text": "that are competing to attract new residents?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 535260.0,
      "text": "This is an idea worth spreading."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 535260.0,
      "end_time": 537260.0,
      "text": "And my friends from Honduras"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 537260.0,
      "end_time": 539260.0,
      "text": "asked me to say thank you, TED."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 539260.0,
      "end_time": 547260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}